        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Rebase the branch onto latest `origin/main` and PR #94702, updating folded scenarios to the dotted QA coverage IDs.\n- Fold the OpenAI-compatible chat tools, OpenAI web_search minimal, native web_search assertion, and OpenWebUI probe script tests into QA Lab native evidence paths.\n- Add QA scenario YAML entries for the folded HTTP/API proof so taxonomy coverage now fulfills `gateway.tool-invocation-api`, `gateway.openai-compatible-apis`, `runtime.reasoning-and-cache-controls`, `web-search.openai-native-web-search`, and `plugins.web-search-and-fetch`.\n- Update changed-test routing so edits to the existing Docker/client scripts run the new QA Lab evidence files.\n- Trim script-era cruft from the folded QA Lab tests while keeping behavior-oriented auth and HTTP API assertions.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openai-compatible-chat-tools.e2e.test.ts test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openai-web-search-minimal.e2e.test.ts test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openai-web-search-minimal-assertions.e2e.test.ts test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openwebui-probe.e2e.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-catalog.test.ts test/scripts/test-projects.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-node.mjs qa coverage --json --output /tmp/openclaw-qa-coverage-rebased-94702.json`\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 qa/scenarios/runtime/openai-compatible-chat-tools.yaml qa/scenarios/runtime/openai-web-search-minimal.yaml qa/scenarios/runtime/openai-web-search-native-assertions.yaml qa/scenarios/runtime/openwebui-openai-compatible.yaml test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openai-compatible-chat-tools.e2e.test.ts test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openai-web-search-minimal.e2e.test.ts test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openai-web-search-minimal-assertions.e2e.test.ts test/e2e/qa-lab/runtime/openwebui-probe.e2e.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-catalog.test.ts test/scripts/test-projects.test.ts scripts/test-projects.test-support.mjs`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extension